{"tid":14558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[邊個申請邊個係...]港府：接獲中央政府通知　部分議員及人士可申回鄉證","createTime":"2016-11-30T14:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T14:54:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"308347d6fbd56593709dc8b7b01b81fe39c78298","tid":14558,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161130/s00001/1480514156427SL4_AC64934D32CD9DD6FA335C8DA85D211A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161130%2Fs00001%2F1480514156427SL4_AC64934D32CD9DD6FA335C8DA85D211A.jpg&h=03bf5d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日消息稱，內地部門日內宣布向曾被拒發回鄉證的泛民主派人士「開綠燈」，幫港出聲一行人今午在北京與國務院港澳事務辦公室主任王光亞見面後，幫港出聲發起人周融今午約4時向傳媒表示，中央政府主管部門已同意沒有回鄉證的反對派人士，可申請證件返回內地，希望他們可回內地旅遊、探親或進行各種形式交流，以增加他們對中國的了解。<br />\n<br />\n至今晚8時，即周融合見傳媒4小時後，香港特區政府發出新聞稿，指接獲中央政府通知，即日起放寬過去對部分立法會議員及其他人士實施進入內地的入境限制，並且重新接受此類人士的《港澳居民來往內地通行證》（俗稱回鄉證）的申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161130/s00001/1480508328553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161130%2Fs00001%2F1480508328553&d=0vu8VjYP3jCE3gO3K89sJxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=8e8ad03e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161130%2Fs00001%2F1480508328553&h=671cd896\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161130/s00001/1480508328553</a>"},{"pid":"d66d47010e1cfcbfa02d187c6a9be489639f5608","tid":14558,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"雪廠街？冚家富？"},{"pid":"295e965927be0823fdeef4d3261a9ee30422ca3d","tid":14558,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n如果真係當香港係自己人既話應該一開始就比歡樂卡佢地<br />\n講到大恩大德咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"